麟Rarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2025-02-28-twin0288.mdﾙ@dfdceaf0ddafbc6902f186229a02b1ff83d01cb31bb22996918cb451c5f02284ﾙ"title: 'This week in Nushell #288'測HighlightsﾚｱWow! What a week!
Huge thanks to cosineblast for the incredible effort in landing one of Nushell's most anticipated and highly

requested features. Support for background jobs has arrived!
A warm welcome to cptpiepmatz and Bahex as the newest members of the core Nushell team! Thank you for all

you have done for our community!
And Nushell is easier to install than ever with official 
``.deb``
, 
``.rpm``
, and 
``.apk``
 packages. See the

[link: https://www.nushell.sh/book/installation.html#package-managers] Installation Guide
 for newly added directions

for Debian, Ubuntu, Redhat/Fedora, Rocky, and Alpine. Thank you hustcer!
As always, thanks to all the contributors this week:
註接潚itle: title: 'This week in Nushell #288'
Path: Highlights
Content:
Wow! What a week!
Huge thanks to cosineblast for the incredible effort in landing one of Nushell's most anticipated and highly

requested features. Support for background jobs has arrived!
A warm welcome to cptpiepmatz and Bahex as the newest members of the core Nushell team! Thank you for all

you have done for our community!
And Nushell is easier to install than ever with official 
``.deb``
, 
``.rpm``
, and 
``.apk``
 packages. See the

[link: https://www.nushell.sh/book/installation.html#package-managers] Installation Guide
 for newly added directions

for Debian, Ubuntu, Redhat/Fedora, Rocky, and Alpine. Thank you hustcer!
As always, thanks to all the contributors this week:
麟Rarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2025-02-28-twin0288.mdﾙ@5f052229521256c8f4c04798a8d7fc3816cfc89e9e4f385e614969e89f410934ﾙ"title: 'This week in Nushell #288'息Nushellﾚ䠖ardfau1t 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15212] fixed 
``test-support``
 to use the 
``CARGO_BUILD_TARGET_DIR``
 env var
.
blindFS made several improvements:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15203] Fixed new Clippy warnings from Rust 1.85.0
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15173] Added semantic tokens for highlighting internal commands with spaces in LSP
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15171] Fixed 
``prefix_str``
 trimming for 
``element_expression``
 in completions
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15169] Fixed edge cases in operator completions
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15086] Refactored 
``flatten_shape``
 to 
``expression``
 for internal/external/operator completions
.
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15192] optimized runtime pipeline input type checking performance
.
fdncred made several updates:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15191] Updated Reedline edit commands in Nushell
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15190] Improved 
``query json``
 help and examples
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15162] Allowed 
``bench``
 to handle larger numbers
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15189] bumped Reedline to its latest commit
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15187] updated 
``ratatui``
 to version 
``0.29.0``
.
dependabot
[
bot
]
 handled dependency updates:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15183] Bumped 
``rust-embed``
 from 8.5.0 to 8.6.0
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15180] Bumped 
``crate-ci/typos``
 from 1.29.5 to 1.29.10
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15179] Bumped 
``actions-rust-lang/setup-rust-toolchain``
 from 1.10.1 to 1.11.0
.
ayax79 made changes to Polars:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15178] Allowed any Polars expression for the 
``pattern``
 argument in 
``polars strip-chars``
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15177] Moved to Polars 
``bigidx``
.
hongquan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15172] improved documentation for the 
``each``
 command
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15166] added benchmarks for 
``insert``
.
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15161] enhanced 
``split list``
 with streaming, closure arguments, and splitting before/after separators
.
cosineblast 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14883] Added jobs functionality
.
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15149] improved precision of 
``ErrorKind::NotFound``
 errors
.
sgvictorino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15140] added signal checks in 
``nu-glob``
 and 
``ls``
.
MMukundi 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15133] fixed 
``insert/upsert``
 creation for nested lists
.
MMesch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15118] added Polars 
``str strip-chars``
 with 
``--end``
 and 
``--start``
 options
.
